      <title>中国开发商恢复英国商业地产撤退</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinese-developers-resume-uk-commercial-property-retreat-2024-03-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[房地产经纪人表示，一些中国大型开发商将出售更多英国房地产以筹集现金，充分利用缓慢解冻的市场和押注复苏的买家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinese-developers-resume-uk-commercial-property-retreat-2024-03-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 06:10:13 GMT</pubDate>
