      <title>中国经济改革令投资者失望，油价延续跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-extends-fall-chinas-pledge-transform-economy-fails-impress-2024-03-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，油价连续第二天下跌，原因是中国承诺在新冠疫情大流行以来增长缓慢的情况下实现经济转型，但未能打动担心消费放缓的投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-extends-fall-chinas-pledge-transform-economy-fails-impress-2024-03-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 02:06:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
